Paper: hep-th/0004046

Date: 2000-04-07

Title: Irreducible Hamiltonian BRST symmetry for reducible first-class systems

Authors: C. Bizdadea, E. M. Cioroianu, S. O. Saliu

Comments: Latex 2.09, 23 pages, to appear in Int. J. Mod. Phys. A

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A15 (2000) 3001-3018

An irreducible Hamiltonian BRST quantization method for reducible first-classsystems is proposed. The general theory is illustrated on a two-stage reduciblemodel, the link with the standard reducible BRST treatment being alsoemphasized.